<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contact Us</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Include the header partial -->
    <%- include('partials/header.ejs') %>

    <div class="content-wrap">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Contact</h1>
            <p>Have a question about a food spot in Singapore, or a suggestion for my next post? I'd be happy to hear from you.</p>
            <p>Please fill out the form below, and I'll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
            <br>
            <p>For a more direct connection, you can also find me on social media:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>TikTok: <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@LionCityBites" target="_blank">@LionCityBites</a></li>
                <li>Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/LionCityBites.SG" target="_blank">@LionCityBites.SG</a></li>
                <li>Pinterest: <a href="https://www.pinterest.com/LionCityBites" target="_blank">pinterest.com/LionCityBites</a></li>
            </ul>
            <br>
            <p>I try to reply to all emails within 72 hours. For direct inquiries, you can also email me at <a href="mailto:alex.tan@lioncitybites.com">alex.tan@lioncitybites.com</a>. Thank you for reaching out.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include the footer partial -->
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>

<style>
    .content-wrap {
        padding: 20px 0;
    }
</style>
</body>
</html>
